  m_Name: Hearing
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalSO
  title: 'Report 3:'
  entry: There is no hope down here. I saw my close friend getting mauled by this
    dark figure. And another friend was attacked. No wounds visible with our sight-
    except he lost his. These beings are cruel. They attack the senses as a cruel
    game.
  number: 0
  image: {fileID: 0}
  playerResponse: Thankfully my ears aren't shot.
